description: KEN05501 - Mainstreaming MDGs in Kenya's Development Process

subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description: The long term outcomes that this project aims at contributing to promote the achievement of the country’s MDG based national development policies and plans (Vision 2030, MTP) through strengthened policy dialogue, sustainable utilization of the environment and natural resources, enhanced budget effectiveness, and strengthened partnerships and linkages across sectors
